Louart Corp , Los Angeles investment firm , said raised stake Amerford International Corp 105,615 share , 7.8 pct total outstanding , 69,715 share , 5.2 pct .
In filing Securities Exchange Commission , Louart said bought 35,900 Amerford common share March 19 , 1986 Jan 30 , 1987 price ranging 3.92 4.29 dlrs share .
It said bought share investment purpose might increase stake future .
